                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1650" notAfter="1699" evidence="prosopography">Second half of the 17th century (?).
                        The colophon (<locus target="#173va"/>) provides a range of dates referring to the end of the 17th century which, however, do not coincide. 
                        One date refers to the second year of the reign of King ʾIyasu (most likely <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5616IyasuI">ʾIyasu I</persName> (=1684 CE).</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>The book belonged to <t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">ʾAbeto</t:roleName> <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14883Abeselom">ʾAbeselom</persName>, 
                     but was donated to <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0105DD">Dabra Dāmmo ʾAbuna ʾAragāwi</placeName> by his mother <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14882Elleni">ʾƎlleni</persName> (see <ref target="#a1">Additio 1</ref>).</provenance>
